$2,159 average, $5.3 million, five weeks. 
</P>
<P>
	15. ``Shakespeare in Love,'' Miramax, $511,368, 572 locations,  
$894 average, $99.4 million, 31 weeks. 
</P>
<P>
	16. ``The Matrix,'' Warner Bros., $510,407, 527 locations, $969  
average, $167.5 million, 15 weeks. 
</P>
<P>
	17. ``Tea With Mussolini,'' MGM, $441,750, 281 locations, $1,572  
average, $11.5 million, nine weeks. 
</P>
