<HEADLINE> Ambrose, Saints Reach 2-Year Deal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW ORLEANS (AP) -- Free agent Ashley Ambrose, a Pro Bowl pick  
with the Cincinnati Bengals in 1996, signed a two-year contract on 
Tuesday with the New Orleans Saints. 
</P>
<P>
